543
01:31:37,990 --> 01:31:41,870
I thought maybe it was not
the proper thing to do.

544
01:31:41,990 --> 01:31:45,630
- Shall I open it?
- No. Give it to me.

545
01:32:51,870 --> 01:32:54,590
