552
01:33:48,670 --> 01:33:50,790
DO YOU LOVE HIM?!

553
01:33:50,910 --> 01:33:52,630
DO YOU?!

554
01:33:54,070 --> 01:33:57,630
- IS IT HIM YOU LOVE?!
