555
01:34:00,830 --> 01:34:03,070
MOTHER!

556
01:34:04,190 --> 01:34:06,070
MOTHER!

557
01:35:02,390 --> 01:35:04,590
Mumma!

558
01:35:08,710 --> 01:35:10,390
You give this to Baines.

559
01:35:11,670 --> 01:35:14,710
Tell him if he ever sees her again,
