590
01:40:49,840 --> 01:40:51,800
Get up.

591
01:40:59,120 --> 01:41:01,200
Baines...

592
01:41:02,960 --> 01:41:05,600
...has Ada ever spoken to you?

593
01:41:07,520 --> 01:41:09,480
You mean in signs?

594
01:41:11,200 --> 01:41:13,320
No. Words.

595
01:41:14,400 --> 01:41:16,600
Have you ever heard words?

596
01:41:17,080 --> 01:41:19,240
No. Not words.

597
01:41:19,760 --> 01:41:22,480
You never thought you heard words?

598
01:41:27,320 --> 01:41:33,240
I heard it here. I heard her voice.
There in my head.

599
01:41:35,200 --> 01:41:38,840
