602
01:41:51,840 --> 01:41:53,760
She said...

603
01:41:57,480 --> 01:42:00,120
"I am afraid of my will...

604
01:42:00,880 --> 01:42:05,200
...of what it might do.
It is so strange and strong."

605
01:42:05,320 --> 01:42:07,240
She said...

606
01:42:09,120 --> 01:42:11,720
"I have to go. Let me go.

607
01:42:12,440 --> 01:42:16,760
Let Baines take me away.
Let him try and save me."

608
01:42:20,480 --> 01:42:23,200
I wish her gone. I wish you gone.

609
01:42:27,640 --> 01:42:29,960
I want to wake up...

610
01:42:31,240 --> 01:42:33,440
...and find that this...

611
01:42:33,560 --> 01:42:36,280
...was all a dream.
That's what I want.

612
01:42:52,240 --> 01:42:54,480
It was a terrible shock.

613
01:42:55,320 --> 01:42:57,640
Oh, dear!

614
01:44:22,400 --> 01:44:25,040
