01:48:53,000 --> 01:48:55,120
<i>'What a surprise!</i>

627
01:49:02,600 --> 01:49:05,400
<i>'My will has chosen life.</i>

628
01:49:16,200 --> 01:49:21,640
<i>'Still, it has had me spooked,
